OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FThe NHS in the south east is to step
OL,7,Fup its action to tackle major
OL,8,Finequalities in cancer care.
OL,10,FOnly 72% of black women were diagnosed
OL,11,Fwith breast cancer at an early stage
OL,12,Fin Kent and Medway - compared to 85%
OL,13,Fof white women.
OL,15,FHealth bosses say they will expand
OL,16,Ftheir diagnosis programme and work
OL,17,Fwith more faith-based and community
OL,18,Fgroups.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
