OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FIn a bid to improve figures - the NHS
OL,7,Fsays it is expanding diagnosis
OL,8,Fprogrammes and looking to reach
OL,9,Fsmaller communities through its Cancer
OL,10,FAlliances initiative.
OL,12,FDr Christopher Tibbs, Regional Medical
OL,13,FDirector for NHS England South East,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The evidence shows that where
OL,15,Fyou live, your background and your
OL,16,Fcircumstances can all influence how
OL,17,Fand when you access cancer services.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
