CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772464379
OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FHe has been working with the
OL,7,FCommunities Against Cancer programme
OL,8,Fand Wessex Cancer Alliance to raise
OL,9,Fawareness of the importance of
OL,10,Fscreening and cancer treatment. "One
OL,11,Fin two people will be diagnosed with
OL,12,Fcancer and my family wasn't an
OL,13,Fexception, with my father diagnosed
OL,14,Fwith cancer. What we did was we
OL,15,Fmanaged to diagnose it early which
OL,16,Fsaved his life. Please don't ignore
OL,17,Fit, please consult your GP," he says.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/11
