OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FThis approach is being strengthened by
OL,7,Flocal organisations such as Kikoi
OL,8,FConnection, which recently ran a
OL,9,Fprostate cancer awareness event in
OL,10,FBasingstoke for Black, African,
OL,11,FCaribbean and Asian communities.
OL,13,FThe event created a safe, culturally
OL,14,Frelevant space for open discussion and
OL,15,Fincreased understanding of prostate
OL,16,Fcancer risks and early testing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
