OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FAttendees reported greater confidence
OL,7,Fin asking questions about prostate
OL,8,Fhealth, screening and early detection
OL,9,F` demonstrating the impact of trusted
OL,10,Fmessengers and communityled
OL,11,Fengagement.
OL,13,FWhile Grace Powell, founder and chair
OL,14,Fof Basingstoke Caribbean Society and
OL,15,FFriends - a group who also work
OL,16,Fclosely with Wessex Cancer Alliance to
OL,17,Fraise awareness of cancer amongst the
OL,18,FCaribbean community encourages people
OL,19,Fto know the signs and listen to their
OL,20,Fbody.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
