OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,F"Don't just write it off as nothing,
OL,7,Fgo and speak to your doctor and get
OL,8,Fmedical advice and learn what the
OL,9,Fsigns and symptoms of cancer are," she
OL,10,Fsays
OL,12,F"Go and speak to your GP and get it
OL,13,Fchecked out. Don't keep it hidden, get
OL,14,Fit sorted nice and early."
