OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FIn Surrey and Sussex, the Cancer
OL,7,FAlliance is expanding its Targeted
OL,8,FLung Health Check programme, which
OL,9,Fidentifies people at higher risk of
OL,10,Flung cancer and offers a free
OL,11,Fassessment and lowdose CT scan if
OL,12,Fneeded.
OL,14,FThe programme is already detecting
OL,15,Fcancers at an earlier stage, when
OL,16,Ftreatment is more effective, and is
OL,17,Fhelping reduce inequalities by
OL,18,Freaching communities with higher
OL,19,Fsmoking prevalence and poorer health
OL,20,Foutcomes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
