PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772464379
OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FNHS teams are working to increase
OL,7,Fawareness of bowel, breast and
OL,8,Fcervical screening, including the
OL,9,Fregion's dedicated Love Your Cervix
OL,10,Fcampaign, which supports national
OL,11,Fambitions to eliminate cervical cancer
OL,12,Fby 2040 and also targets women from
OL,13,Fethnic minority backgrounds who are
OL,14,Fless likely to attend screening
OL,15,Fappointments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
