PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772464379
OL,3,CNHS in South East aims to tackle major
OL,4,Cinequalities in cancer care
OL,6,FDr Daghni Rajasingam, Deputy Regional
OL,7,FMedical Director, for NHS England
OL,8,FSouth East added: "Communityled
OL,9,Finitiatives like Communities Against
OL,10,FCancer and the work of groups such as
OL,11,FKikoi Connection show the power of
OL,12,Ftrusted voices in breaking down stigma
OL,13,Fand reaching people who may not
OL,14,Fotherwise come forward.
OL,16,F"Combined with targeted programmes
OL,17,Flike lung health checks and the Love
OL,18,FYour Cervix campaign, this is how we
OL,19,Fclose the gap and deliver fairer
OL,20,Foutcomes for everyone."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
